# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#ContaminationRisk
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#ContaminationRisk> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#ContaminationRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Risk> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#ContaminationRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Riesgo de contaminación del producto o de sus reactivos."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#ContaminationRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Contamination Risk"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#CorrectiveAction
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#CorrectiveAction> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#CorrectiveAction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatedEntity> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#CorrectiveAction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Acción correctiva de seguridad en campo (FSCA) emprendida por el fabricante para reducir el riesgo asociado a un dispositivo comercializado."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#CorrectiveAction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Field Safety Corrective Action"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Country
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Country> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Country> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatedEntity> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Country> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Estado en el que opera un fabricante, se notifica un incidente o se ve afectada una acción correctiva."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Country> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Country"@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Country> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Country> .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#CybersecurityRisk
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#CybersecurityRisk> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#CybersecurityRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Risk> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#CybersecurityRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Riesgo derivado de vulnerabilidades de ciberseguridad del dispositivo."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#CybersecurityRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Cybersecurity Risk"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#DiagnosticRisk
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#DiagnosticRisk> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#DiagnosticRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Risk> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#DiagnosticRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Riesgo específico de dispositivos IVD: falsos positivos, falsos negativos, reactividad cruzada, etc."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#DiagnosticRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Diagnostic Risk"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#HighRiskClassCategory
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#HighRiskClassCategory> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#HighRiskClassCategory> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RiskClass> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#HighRiskClassCategory> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Metacategoría que agrupa las clases de riesgo más altas (ClassIII en MDR, ClassD en IVDR) y que se usa como disparador de la regla SWRL de HighRiskDevice."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#HighRiskClassCategory> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "High Risk Class Category"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#HighRiskDevice
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#HighRiskDevice> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#HighRiskDevice> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#MedicalDevice> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#HighRiskDevice> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Clase inferida que agrupa los dispositivos con clase de riesgo más alta (ClassIII bajo MDR o ClassD bajo IVDR). Se puebla mediante regla SWRL."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#HighRiskDevice> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "High Risk Device"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#IVDRFramework
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#IVDRFramework> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#IVDRFramework> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatoryFramework> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#IVDRFramework> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Regulation (EU) 2017/746 on in vitro diagnostic medical devices."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#IVDRFramework> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "IVDR Framework"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#IVDRRiskClass
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#IVDRRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
