<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#IVDRRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#disjointWith> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#MDRRiskClass> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#IVDRRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Clase de riesgo bajo el reglamento IVDR (A, B, C, D)."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#IVDRRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "IVDR Risk Class"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#ImplantableActiveDevice
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#ImplantableActiveDevice> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
