<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#InjuryRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Risk> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#InjuryRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Riesgo de daño directo al paciente."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#InjuryRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Injury Risk"@en .
