<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RadiationRisk> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RadiationRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Risk> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RadiationRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Riesgo asociado a la exposición inadvertida o excesiva a radiación ionizante o no ionizante."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RadiationRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Radiation Risk"@en .
