<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Recall> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Retirada de producto del mercado."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Recall> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Recall"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RecalledDevice
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RecalledDevice> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
