<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatedEntity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatedEntity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Regulated Entity"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatoryFramework
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatoryFramework> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatoryFramework> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatedEntity> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatoryFramework> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Reglamento europeo bajo el que se clasifica y vigila un dispositivo."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatoryFramework> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Regulatory Framework"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Risk
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Risk> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Risk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatedEntity> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Risk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Riesgo identificado que puede asociarse a un tipo de dispositivo, codificado conforme a la nomenclatura IMDRF."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#Risk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Risk"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RiskClass
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RegulatedEntity> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Categoría de riesgo asignada a un dispositivo conforme al anexo correspondiente del MDR o del IVDR."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#RiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Risk Class"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#SafetyAlert
