<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#SafetyAlert> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Comunicación de seguridad sin retirada del producto."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#SafetyAlert> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Safety Alert"@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#SelfTestDevice
<http://www.semanticweb.org/ontologies/eudamed-mdr-ivdr#SelfTestDevice> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
